FOR 	
Reference (18 bytes):

		FOR Marker 				[1]
		Page/Position for loop 	[3]
		Control 				[1] 	Integer/Int16 ; optimised 
		Index Variable 			[2] 
		Step (+1 optimise) 		[6]
		Terminal Value.	 		[6]

Token list (standard)		
=====================
FOR NEXT DATA INPUT# INPUT DIM READ RESTORE ON WAIT LOAD DEF POKE PRINT# CMD SYS OPEN CLOSE GET FN

Token list (X16)
================
VPOKE VLOAD SCREEN PSET LINE FRAME RECT CHAR MOUSE COLOR TEST RESET CLS LOCATE
BLOAD BVLOAD BVERIFY BANK VPEEK MX MY MB JOY 

HEX$ BIN$ (untested)

<const> <ref!> <ref> <terminal> <step> .for  ...... .next

